This directory is the build output staged for Workshop publish.
Build the project with `dotnet build -c Release` to populate it. Contents are produced
by the StageWorkshopBuild target in WorldCustomizer.csproj.

Expected contents after a clean Release build:
  WorldCustomizer.dll
  WorldCustomizer.pdb
  0Harmony.dll
  preview.png    (when workshop-assets/preview.png exists)

To publish to Steam Workshop, point the in-game upload tool at this folder.
